{"tid":1719184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天水圍15歲少年疑被催淚彈擊中頭部　開腦手術後情況危殆","createTime":"2019-11-14T04:45:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T15:41:46.000Z","uid":13663,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"b0bc47d96208f65bbb8276e2daee23030259e37a","tid":1719184,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:45:28.000Z","msg":"昨晚天水圍警署外有大批示威者聚集，期間有人投擲汽油彈，防暴警察向新北江商場人群發射催淚彈驅散。一名15歲少年懷疑被催淚彈擊中頭部昏迷，送屯門醫院搶救，經手術後情況危殆，現時在深切治療部留醫。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果日報》報道，<span style=\"color: red;\">少年父母已經逝世</span>，其叔父向該報表示，事發時沒記者在場，他希望知道侄仔是無辜被警察打中，還是參與激進行為，呼籲大家「幫幫手」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1000bc26191db9e6b23e88a0c17a5bf2221b52f","tid":1719184,"uid":81698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:47:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db1a591748a3b9be7a7268c914d305a887bbdce","tid":1719184,"uid":148262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:47:18.000Z","msg":"手足啊😭😭😭😭"},{"pid":"2ab41f31f8998c48f4c6dad59dd9d2ef75f0c990","tid":1719184,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:47:52.000Z","msg":"[文宣升級&mdash;要追上前線行動呀！]<br />\n解鎖新職業 &mdash; 郵差叔叔，速遞員！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1717313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1717313</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，手足，借個位，認同請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發生好多事，好多怨案，令我地好嬲好嬲。但文宣一定要做足做好，我地係為正義而戰，我地從來都唔係暴徒！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/arAivP6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FarAivP6.png&h=a9a1a627&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zSLZfgM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzSLZfgM.jpg&h=20bdb60e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d344f42277ccedae4110a03cdcd42cb8c19cb5c2","tid":1719184,"uid":21101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:48:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5be3f156f7ca51e1ffb1b1e61f42dd876a3a37c3","tid":1719184,"uid":8011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:48:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不能有事！！！！！"},{"pid":"7b4fd742559489b58581de615b8b40cfa84ec130","tid":1719184,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:49:24.000Z","msg":"不能再死 求下你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c21b3e2bee6bac360ab53c5ea63c1c21a99be5","tid":1719184,"uid":223146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:49:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449cebe946f24b9d857cb07088205bd2437ef1d2","tid":1719184,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:50:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\